{
  "chapter": "076",
  "title": "平原君虞卿列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "平原君其人",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵胜</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国的众<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公子</span>之一。<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">诸子</span>之中，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胜\">胜（赵胜）</span>最为贤能，喜好结交<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>，归附他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>达到<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数千人</span>之多。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>做过<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵惠文王</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵孝成王\">孝成王（赵孝成王）</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>，三次离开相位，又三次复职，被封在东<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武城</span>。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "斩美人谢门客",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>家的楼阁俯临<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>家。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>家有个跛脚的人，一瘸一拐地去打水。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">美人</span>住在楼上，俯身看见，大笑嘲弄他。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">明日</span>，跛脚的人来到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>门前，请求说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>听说<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>喜好<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人不远<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千里</span>前来投奔的原因，是因为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>能尊崇<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人而看轻姬妾。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>不幸患有瘸腿的病，而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>的后宫却俯身嘲笑<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>希望得到嘲笑<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>的那个人的头。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>笑着答应说：\"好。\" 跛脚的人离开后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>笑着说：\"看这<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">竖子</span>，竟想因为一笑之故就让我<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>掉<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">美人</span>，不也太过分了吗！\" 终究没有<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>她。过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">岁馀（时长）</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">门下</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">舍人</span>逐渐离去的超过了一半。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>感到奇怪，说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胜\">胜（赵胜）</span>待各位<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>子从未敢失<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>，可是离去的人怎么这么多呢？\" <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">门下</span>有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>上前回答说：\"因为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>不<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>那个嘲笑跛脚者的人，大家以为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>是贪恋美色而看轻<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人就离开了。\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>就<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>下了嘲笑跛脚者的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">美人</span>的头，亲自送到跛脚者门前谢罪。此后<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">门下</span>才又逐渐来归附。这时<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">孟尝（孟尝君）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：信陵君\">信陵（信陵君）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：春申君\">春申（春申君）</span>，所以各国<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公子</span>都争相招揽<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "毛遂自荐",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>去求<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">救</span>兵，想与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">合从</span>，约定在<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">食客</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">门下</span>中挑选有勇力、文武兼备者<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十人</span>一同前往。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>说：\"如果凭文治能达成<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胜\">胜（赵胜）</span>的目的，那是最好。文治达不成目的，就在华丽宫殿之下歃血为盟，一定要订立盟约才回来。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>不必外求，就从<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">食客</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">门下</span>中挑选就够了。\" 得到<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十九人</span>，其余没有可取的，凑不足<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十人</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">门下</span>有个叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">毛遂</span>的，上前，自荐于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：毛遂\">遂（毛遂）</span>听说<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>将要与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">合从</span>，约定在<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">食客</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">门下</span>中挑选<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十人</span>同行，不向外求。现在还缺<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>，愿<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>就让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：毛遂\">遂（毛遂）</span>凑个数一起去吧。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>说：\"先生在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胜\">胜（赵胜）</span>门下几年了？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">毛遂</span>说：\"在这里<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>了。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>说：\"贤能的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人处世，就像锥子放在口袋里，锥尖立刻显露出来。现在先生在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胜\">胜（赵胜）</span>门下<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>了，左右的人未曾称颂过先生，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胜\">胜（赵胜）</span>也未曾听说过先生，这是先生没有什么才能。先生不行，先生留下吧。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">毛遂</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>就是<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">今日</span>才请求放进口袋里罢了。若让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：毛遂\">遂（毛遂）</span>早早放进口袋中，就会整个锥子都脱颖而出，不仅仅是锥尖显露而已。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>终于与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">毛遂</span>一同前往。<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十九人</span>相互以眼神嘲笑他，但没有废除他。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "毛遂按剑定从",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">毛遂</span>到了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国，和<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十九人</span>谈论议事，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十九人</span>都佩服他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王商议<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">合从</span>，陈说其中的利害，从日出就开始谈，到<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">日中</span>还没有决定。<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十九人</span>对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">毛遂</span>说：\"先生上去吧。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">毛遂</span>手按<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>沿台阶而上，对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>说：\"合从的利害，两句话就能决定。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">今日</span>出来谈合从，到<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">日中</span>还不能决定，这是为什么呢？\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>说：\"这位客人是做什么的？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>说：\"这是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胜\">胜（赵胜）</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">舍人</span>。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王喝斥说：\"<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>不下去！我是和你<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>说话，你算什么东西！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">毛遂</span>按<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>上前说：\"大王之所以喝斥<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：毛遂\">遂（毛遂）</span>，是倚仗<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国人多势众。现在十步之内，大王不能倚仗<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国的人多势众了，大王的性命悬在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：毛遂\">遂（毛遂）</span>手里。我<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>就在前面，喝斥什么？况且<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：毛遂\">遂（毛遂）</span>听说商汤凭<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">七十里</span>之地称王于<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周文王\">文王（周文王）</span>凭<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百里</span>之地使<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>称<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>，难道是他们的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒众多吗？实在是因为能依据形势奋发威力。现在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国土地方圆<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五千里</span>，持戟的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒百万，这是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">霸王</span>的资本。凭<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国的强大，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>没有谁能抵挡。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span>，不过是个小<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">竖子</span>，率<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数万</span>之众，兴师与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>，一<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>就<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">举</span>占了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鄢郢</span>，再〖◈战就<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">烧了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">夷陵</span>，三<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>就侮辱了大王的先祖。这是<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">百世（时长）</span>的仇怨，也是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国都为之羞愧的，可大王却不知羞耻。<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">合从</span>是为了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国，不是为了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国。我<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>就在前面，喝斥什么？\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王说：\"是是，确实如先生所言，我恭敬地奉<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">社稷</span>而参与合从。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">毛遂</span>说：\"合从决定了吗？\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王说：\"决定了。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">毛遂</span>对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王的左右侍从说：\"<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>鸡、狗、<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>的血来。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">毛遂</span>捧着<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">铜槃</span>跪着献给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王说：\"大王应当歃血定下合从，其次是我<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>，再次是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：毛遂\">遂（毛遂）</span>。\" 于是在殿上确定了合从。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">毛遂</span>左手端着<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">槃</span>血，右手招呼〖$十九人</span>说：\"诸位相互在堂下歃血吧。诸位庸庸碌碌，这就是所谓依靠别人成事。\""
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "以毛遂为上客",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>已经定下合从回到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国后，说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胜\">胜（赵胜）</span>不敢再识<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胜\">胜（赵胜）</span>识<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>多则<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千人</span>，少也有百数，自以为不会错过<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人，今天却在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：毛遂\">毛先生（毛遂）</span>这里错过了。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：毛遂\">毛先生（毛遂）</span>一到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国，使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国的地位重于九<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">鼎</span>和<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">大吕</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：毛遂\">毛先生（毛遂）</span>凭<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三寸</span>之舌，强过百万大军。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胜\">胜（赵胜）</span>不敢再识<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>了。\" 于是把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">毛遂</span>作为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上客</span>。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "李同敢死解邯郸",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>回到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国以后，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>领兵<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">赴救</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">信陵君</span>也矫命夺取了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋鄙</span>的军队前去<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">救</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，都还未到。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军加紧<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>形势危急，将要<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">降</span>敌，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>非常忧虑。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>传舍吏的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李同</span>劝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>不忧虑<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">亡</span>吗？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国亡了则<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胜\">胜（赵胜）</span>就成俘虏，怎么会不忧虑呢？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李同</span>说：\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众，烧骨头当柴烧，交换<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>女当食物吃，可以说危急到了极点，然而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>的后宫有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百数</span>之多，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">婢妾</span>们都穿着<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">绮縠</span>，享用精米肉食，而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众连<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">褐衣</span>都穿不完整，连糟糠都吃不饱。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>困兵尽，有的削木为<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">矛矢</span>，而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>的器物<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">锺磬</span>完好如初。假使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>哪里还能拥有这些？假使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>能保全，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>何愁没有呢？现在<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>如果真能让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>以下都编入<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒之间，分担劳作，家中所有的都拿出来犒劳<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒正处于危苦之时，就容易感恩了。\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>听从他的建议，得到敢死的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三千人</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李同</span>就率领<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三千人</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">赴</span>击<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军为此退却了<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三十里</span>。也恰逢<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>的<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">救</span>兵到了，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>兵于是撤退，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>得以保存。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李同</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战死</span>了，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>亲为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">李侯</span>。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "公孙龙止请封",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>想凭<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">信陵君</span>保存<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>的功劳为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>请求<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>地。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙龙</span>听说后，连夜驾车去见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙龙\">龙（公孙龙）</span>听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>想凭<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">信陵君</span>保存<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>的功劳为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>请求<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>地，有这事吗？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>说：\"是的。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙龙\">龙（公孙龙）</span>说：\"这万万不可。大王任用<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>，并非因为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>的才智是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国独一无二的。割东<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武城</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>，并非因为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>有什么功绩，而是因为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">国人</span>没有功勋，就因为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">亲戚</span>的缘故。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>接受相<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">印</span>不推辞自己无能，接受封地不推辞自己无功，也是自认为是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">亲戚</span>的缘故。现在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">信陵君</span>保存<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>而请求<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>地，是让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">亲戚</span>受封城池而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">国人</span>按功劳计算。这万万不可。况且<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>操持两手准备：事情成了，就拿着右<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">券</span>来索债；事情不成，就用虚名施恩于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>一定不要听从。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>于是不听<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>的意见。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "平原君卒",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵孝成王\">孝成王（赵孝成王）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十五年</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">卒</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子孙</span>相继承袭，后来最终与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国一同<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">亡</span>国。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "公孙龙见绌",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>厚待<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙龙</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙龙</span>擅长<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">坚白之辩</span>，等到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">邹衍</span>经过<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国谈论<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">至道</span>，就贬抑了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙龙</span>。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "虞卿游说",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>，是个游说的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>。他穿着<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">蹻</span>、拿着<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">簦</span>游说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵孝成王\">孝成王（赵孝成王）</span>。第一次见面，赐给他<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">黄金</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百镒</span>、白<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">璧</span>一双；第二次见面，被任命为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上卿</span>，所以号称<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "长平败兵",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长平</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国失利，损失了一名<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">都尉</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王召见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楼昌</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>说：\"军队<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>不胜，都尉又[死，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span>想让全军装束兵甲奔赴前线，你们看怎么样？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楼昌</span>说：\"没有用处，不如派重要的使者去议和。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楼昌\">昌（楼昌）</span>说议和，是认为不议和军队必<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>。而议和的主动权在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国。况且王认为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国是想<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>军呢，还是不想？\" 王说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国不遗余力，必定要<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>军。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>说：\"王听<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>的话，派使臣带着<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">重宝</span>去结交<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>想得到王的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">重宝</span>，必定会接纳我们的使臣。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>使进入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国必定怀疑<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>要<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">合从</span>，一定会恐慌。这样，议和就可以谈成。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王不听，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵豹\">平阳君（赵豹）</span>去议和，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郑硃</span>到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国接纳了他。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王召见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>说：\"寡人派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵豹\">平阳君（赵豹）</span>到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国议和，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国已经接纳了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郑硃</span>，你看怎么样？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>回答说：\"大王不会议和成功的，军队必<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>无疑。<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>祝贺〖◈战胜的使臣都在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郑硃</span>是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贵人</span>，进入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国后，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王和<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">应侯</span>必定隆重礼遇他以示<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>以为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国议和成功，必不会<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">救</span>王。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国知道<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">救</span>王，议和就不能成功。\" <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">应侯</span>果然隆重礼遇<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郑硃</span>以示<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>祝贺〖◈战胜的人，终究不肯议和。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长平</span>大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>，于是又<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>，被<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>所耻笑。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "赵郝议割地",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国解除<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>困后，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝见，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵郝</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国约定割让<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六城</span>议和。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>大王，是疲倦了才回去的吗？还是其力量还可以继续进攻，只是爱惜大王才不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>的呢？\" 王说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>我，不遗余力，必是因疲倦而归。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国用全力<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>其所不能<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>的地方，疲倦而归，大王又把秦力所不能取的地方送给他们，这是帮助<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国来<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打自己。明年<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国再来<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>大王，大王就没救了。\" 王把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>的话告诉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵郝</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵郝</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>真的能探知<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>力所能达到的极限吗？真的知道<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>力所不能继续进攻，这弹丸之地不给，让<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国明年再来<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>大王，大王能不割让国内之地来求和吗？\" 王说：\"请听从<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>的意见割地，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>能保证明年<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国不再<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>我吗？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵郝</span>回答说：\"这不是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>敢担保的。从前三<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>国与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国交好，关系很好。现在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国友善<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>而<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>大王，大王侍奉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国必定比不上<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>。现在<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>为足下解除失去亲善所招致的<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打，开关通货，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>交<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，到明年而大王独自受到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>的<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打，这是大王侍奉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国必定不如<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>的缘故。这不是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>敢担保的。\""
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "虞卿论割地",
      "text": "王把这话告诉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>回答说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵郝\">郝（赵郝）</span>说'不议和，明年<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国再来<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>大王，大王能不割让国内之地议和吗'。现在议和，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵郝\">郝（赵郝）</span>又不能保证<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国不再<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打。现在虽然割<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六城</span>，有什么用！明年再来<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>，又割让他力所不能取的地方议和，这是自取灭亡之术，不如不议和。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国虽然善于<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>战，不能<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>六县；<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国虽然不能守，终究不会丢失<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六城</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国疲倦而归，兵必疲惫。我以<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六城</span>收买<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>来<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打疲惫的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国，这是我失之于<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>而取偿于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国。我国还有利，与其坐着割地，自己削弱而使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国强大，哪个更好？现在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵郝\">郝（赵郝）</span>说'<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国友善<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>而<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，必定是大王侍奉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国不如<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>'，这是让大王每年用<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六城</span>侍奉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国，坐等城邑尽失。明年<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国再要求割地，大王将给吗？不给，是抛弃以前的功劳而挑起<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>的祸患；给，则没有地可给。俗语说'强者善于<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打，弱者不能防守'。现在坐着听从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>兵不疲惫而多得土地，这是使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国强大而使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国削弱。以日益强大的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国割取日益削弱的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国的土地，这样的计谋是不会停止的。况且大王的土地有尽头而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国的索求没有止境，以有尽的土地去满足无尽的索求，其势必无<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国了。\""
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "楼缓主予秦",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王计策未定，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楼缓</span>从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国来，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楼缓</span>商议，说：\"给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国土地和不给，哪个更吉？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楼缓\">缓（楼缓）</span>推辞说：\"这不是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>所能知道的。\" 王说：\"虽然这样，试着说说公的私见。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楼缓</span>回答说：\"大王听说过<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公甫文伯</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲吗？<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公甫文伯</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>国做官，病死了，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>中为他<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">自杀</span>在房中的有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span>。他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲听说后，不为他哭。他的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相室</span>说：'哪有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>死了而不哭的呢？'他<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲说：'<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>是贤人，被逐出<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>国，这个人不跟随。现在他死了而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妇人</span>为他<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">自杀</span>的有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span>，像他这样必定是对<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长者</span>薄情而对<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妇人</span>厚情。'所以从<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲的口中说出来，这是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贤母</span>；从<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妻</span>子的口中说出，必定不<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">免</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妒妻</span>。所以同样的话，说的人不同<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">人心</span>就变了。现在<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>刚从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国来而说不要给，不是好计策；说要给，恐怕大王认为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>是为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国说话：所以不敢回答。假使让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>为大王考虑，不如给他。\" 王说：\"好。\""
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "楼缓反驳虞卿",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>听说后，入宫见王说：\"这是粉饰之辞，王千万不要给！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楼缓</span>听说后，又去见王。 王又把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>的话告诉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楼缓</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楼缓</span>回答说：\"不是这样。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>只知其一，不知其二。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>构成冤仇而<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>都高兴，为什么呢？他们说'我们要因强者而乘弱者'。现在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>兵被<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国围困，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>祝贺〖◈战胜的使臣必定尽在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国了。所以不如赶快割地议和，以使<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>生疑而安慰<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国之心。不然，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>将利用<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>的愤怒，乘<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>的疲敝，瓜分<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国将亡，还图谋什么<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国？所以说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>只知其一，不知其二。希望大王就此决定，不要再议。\""
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "虞卿赂齐制秦",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>听说后，前去见王说：\"危险啊<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楼缓\">楼子（楼缓）</span>的为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>之计，这是更加让<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>生疑，又怎么能安慰<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国之心呢？难道没说清楚这是示<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>以弱吗？况且<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>说不要给，不是固执地不给而已。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国向大王索取<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六城</span>，而大王把<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六城</span>贿赂<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国的深仇，得到大王的<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六城</span>，并力西进<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国听大王的，话说不完就同意了。这是大王失之于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国而取偿于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国。而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>的深仇可以报了，又向<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>显示有所作为。大王这样宣告，兵还未出境，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>就会看到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">重赂</span>到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国反而请求议和。既然和<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>议和了，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>听说后，必定都尊重大王；尊重大王，必定拿出<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">重宝</span>抢先讨好大王。这样大王一举结交三国之亲，而与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国互换了处境。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王说：\"好。\" 就派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>东去见<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王，一同谋议对付<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>还没回来，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使者</span>已到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国了。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楼缓</span>听说后，逃走了。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一城</span>。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "合魏为从",
      "text": "过了不久，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国请求合从。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵孝成王\">孝成王（赵孝成王）</span>召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>商议。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>路过<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>处，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>说：\"希望听听卿对合从的议论。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>入宫见王。王说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国请求合从。\" 回答说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>错了。\" 王说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span>本来没有答应。\" 回答说：\"大王错了。\" 王说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>请求合从，卿说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>错，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span>没答应，又说<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span>错，那么合从终究不可以吗？\" 回答说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>听说小国与大国共事，有利则大国受其福，有<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>则小国受其祸。现在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>以小国请求担祸，而大王以大国推辞得福，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>所以说大王错，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>也错。私下里认为合从有利。\" 王说：\"好。\" 于是就与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国合从。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "困于大梁著书",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>因<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏齐</span>的缘故，不重<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万户</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">卿相</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">印</span>，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏齐</span>偷偷逃走，终于离开<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国，困于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏齐</span>已<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">死</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>不得志，就著书立说，上采<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">春秋</span>，下观近世，写有<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">节义</span>、<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">称号</span>、<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">揣摩</span>、<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">政谋</span>等，共<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">八篇</span>。以此<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">刺</span>讥国家得失，世上流传叫做<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">虞氏春秋</span>。"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>，是翩翩浊世中的佳<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公子</span>，然而没看到大局。鄙俗的俗语说\"利令智昏\"，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>贪图<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冯亭</span>的邪说，使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国陷于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长平</span>损失士兵四十多万，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>几乎灭亡。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>料事揣情，为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国出谋划策，多么精妙啊！等到不忍舍弃<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏齐</span>，最终困于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大梁</span>，连庸夫都知道不可以，何况贤人呢？然而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>若不穷困忧愁，也不能著书在后世自见。"
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "翩翩<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公子</span>，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>奇器。 笑姬从<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">戮</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">义士</span>增气。 兵解<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李同</span>，盟定<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">毛遂</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>蹑蹻，受赏料事。 及困<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏齐</span>，著书见意。"
    }
  }
}